{"about_the_game":"Stardiver is a sci-fi, single-player, action-adventure game where you pilot a ship and shoot at enemies. The game takes place entirely underwater.<br><br>Stardiver will take you to an unknown world in which you\u2019ll experience exciting fights, discover new species and places. And you\u2019ll take care of resources supply, crafting in your base, and developing your own ship.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PILOT A SHIP</h2>You become a pilot, explorer, scientist, and judge responsible for the planet's fate. Swim around, take a closer look at fauna and flora of the underwater environment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_ship.gif?t=1726748418\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIGHT MONSTERS</h2>The underwater world is beautiful but also very dangerous. Beware of deadly monsters that are hidden in deep water.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_Medusaur2.gif?t=1726748418\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMBAT ENEMY SHIPS</h2>Fight in exciting, underwater battles. Experience spontaneous small battles when searching for new resources. And prepare before engaging a stronger enemy.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_Fight.gif?t=1726748418\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE THE PLANET</h2>Explore this wonderful world. Discover new species and fantastic places. Study ancient ruins and what\u2019s left after an old civilization. Admire the beauty and learn the history of this world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_Scan.gif?t=1726748418\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CRAFT ITEMS</h2>Gather resources by yourself or place auto-mining equipment to do it when you\u2019re busy with other things. Remember that without them you won\u2019t get stronger. And you\u2019re not the only one that wants them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_Craft.gif?t=1726748418\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GATHER RESOURCES</h2>Build mines in discovered places. Create new weapons for your ship. Everything that will make your life easier here. Find out who left it. And why...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599070/extras/Stardiver_resources.gif?t=1726748418\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Scout","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/375c2ed2a2a6b8eca5f35dc2ca86233bfacd872a.jpg"},{"name":"Wild Life Researcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/046e311d7f98c1058da4dbd3864e9d2e8aa5097a.jpg"},{"name":"Fighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/168f13d9a9bafe7e018e67bbfa05a716e63b9f48.jpg"},{"name":"Tough Fighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/04ed794626e1f309b2ed7966c9c0d4653f3e162c.jpg"},{"name":"Killer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/f53780f148fee527f7ce52a6093112eb3935635b.jpg"},{"name":"Killing Machine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/2affe41e8f66f149f14018abdb1a072edf5dfe96.jpg"},{"name":"Battler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/86086040d94c9a437f5a7ae646f8083d44266fc5.jpg"},{"name":"Experienced Fighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/91d244b54940b3dbe225cf086bae375075a4602e.jpg"},{"name":"Terminator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1599070/866f6f84da52ffffafdc77f53acaec698e1bce9f.jpg"},{"n